WEBVTT

15:46.880 --> 15:47.960 line:80%
Thank you, Lord Li.

15:50.160 --> 15:51.080 line:80%
I am humbled.

15:51.520 --> 15:52.590 line:80%
The rebels are rampant.

15:52.590 --> 15:53.430 line:80%
After Mr. Mu He of Jizhou

15:53.430 --> 15:55.280 line:80%
went to guard Lucheng personally,

15:55.280 --> 15:58.810 line:80%
